    <li>The education of one child.</li>
    <li>A charitable contribution each year.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Completed</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Helped eligible families below the poverty line access the Ayushman
      Bharat health insurance scheme.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Focus ahead</h2>
  <p>
    To sustain these commitments, and to take on new work only when it can be
    done properly.
  </p>
